# Life OS Monorepo

**Canonical repo:** `Ken-pan/life-os` at `/Users/kenpan/「Projects」/life-os`

| App     | Path           | Workspace name | Netlify site  | 备注         |
| ------- | -------------- | -------------- | ------------- | ------------ |
| Planner | `apps/planner` | `planner-os`   | kenos-plan | 生产         |
| Fitness | `apps/fitness` | `fitness-os`   | kenos-training | 生产         |
| Finance | `apps/finance` | `finance-os`   | kenos-money | 生产         |
| Music   | `apps/music`   | `music-os`     | kenos-music   | 生产         |
| Portal  | `apps/portal`  | `portal`       | portal-ken    | 生产（I-P1） |
| Home    | `apps/home`    | `home-os`      | kenos-home    | 实验 WIP     |

Shared: `packages/theme`, `packages/sync`, `packages/contracts`, `packages/platform-web`.

Roadmap: `docs/LIFEOS_ROADMAP.md`

## Commands (repo root)

```bash
npm install
npm run build          # turbo — all apps
npm run build:planner  # single app
cd apps/planner && npm run dev
```

## Do not

- Edit legacy archived repos (`planner-os`, `fitness-os`, `Moneymoneymoney`, `MusicOS`, `life-os-theme`, `life-os-sync`).
- Add `file:../life-os-theme` or vendored `packages/life-os-*` in this monorepo.
- Put nested `.github/workflows` under `apps/*` — CI lives at repo root.

## Deploy

Push `master` → Netlify Git build (path ignore per app). Docs: `docs/ops/netlify.md`, `docs/ops/canonical.md`, hub `docs/LIFEOS_ROADMAP.md`.
